  "title": "*New* Enrolled Nurse / Staff Nurse (Full Time / Part Time / Flexi Hours, 5 Days, Office Hours) #HJG",
  "description": "<h2>Job Responsibilities</h2><ul><li><p>Assist and chaperone doctors during clinical consultations and procedures</p></li><li><p>Monitor and record patients’ conditions and progress according to care plans</p></li><li><p>Carry out and document nursing care activities in accordance with clinical protocols</p></li><li><p>Support basic patient registration and billing-related administrative processes</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with healthcare teams to ensure continuity of patient care</p></li></ul><h2>Job Requirements</h2><ul><li><p>Min GCE N/O or ‘A’ Levels / Diploma and above</p></li><li><p>Keen interest in the healthcare/medical industry</p></li><li><p>Basic knowledge of Microsoft Office</p></li><li><p>Able to start work immediately</p></li></ul><p>If you are interested in this position, do kindly drop your most updated resume to <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">joshua.gan@recruitexpress.com.sg</a> and <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">leonleong@recruitexpress.com.sg</a> (Attn: Nursing)</p><p>Leon Leong De Cong<br />R1551708<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifesciences Division)<br />EA License: 99C4599</p>",
